doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=edge')
    meta(name='description', content='A portfolio template that uses Material Design Lite.')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0')
    title MDL-Static Website
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:regular,bold,italic,thin,light,bolditalic,black,medium&lang=en')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://code.getmdl.io/1.3.0/material.grey-pink.min.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/styles.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons')
  body
    .mdl-layout.mdl-js-layout.mdl-layout--fixed-header
      header.mdl-layout__header.mdl-layout__header--waterfall.portfolio-header
        .mdl-layout__header-row.portfolio-logo-row
          span.mdl-layout__title
            .portfolio-logo
            |  
            span.mdl-layout__title Memo
        .demo-drawer.mdl-layout__drawer.mdl-color--blue-grey-900.mdl-color-text--blue-grey-50
          nav.mdl-navigation.mdl-typography--body-1-force-preferred-font
            a.mdl-navigation__link(href='/') Portfolio
            |  
            a.mdl-navigation__link.is-active(href='/blog') Blog
            |  
            a.mdl-navigation__link(href='/notes/write') write
      .demo-drawer.mdl-layout__drawer.mdl-color--blue-grey-900.mdl-color-text--blue-grey-50
        nav.mdl-navigation.mdl-typography--body-1-force-preferred-font
          a.mdl-navigation__link.is-active(href='/') Portfolio
          |  
          a.mdl-navigation__link(href='/blog') Blog
          |  
          a.mdl-navigation__link(href='/notes/write') write
      main.mdl-layout__content
        .mdl-grid.portfolio-max-width
          .mdl-grid.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--12-col.mdl-cell--4-col-tablet.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--4dp
            .mdl-card__media.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--12-col-tablet
              img.article-image(src=' ../images/example-blog01.jpg', border='0', alt='')
            .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--8-col
              h2.mdl-card__title-text Velit anim eiusmod labore sit amet
              .mdl-card__supporting-text.padding-top
                span Posted 2 days ago
                #tt1.icon.material-icons.portfolio-share-btn share
                .mdl-tooltip(for='tt1')  Share via social media
              .mdl-card__supporting-text.no-left-padding
                p
                  | Excepteur reprehenderit sint exercitation ipsum consequat qui sit id velit elit. Velit anim eiusmod labore sit amet. Voluptate voluptate irure occaecat deserunt incididunt esse in. Qui ullamco consectetur aute fugiat officia ullamco proident Lorem ad irure. Sint eu ut consectetur ut esse veniam laboris adipisicing aliquip minim anim labore commodo.
                |  
                span
                  | Category: 
                  a(href='#') Latest
          .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--6-col.mdl-cell--4-col-tablet.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--4dp
            .mdl-card__title
              h2.mdl-card__title-text Voluptate voluptate
            .mdl-card__media
              a(href='#')
                img.article-image(src=' ../images/example-blog02.jpg', border='0', alt='')
            .mdl-card__supporting-text.no-bottom-padding
              span Posted 2 days ago
              #tt2.icon.material-icons.portfolio-share-btn share
              .mdl-tooltip(for='tt2')  Share via social media
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              p
                | Excepteur reprehenderit sint exercitation ipsum consequat qui sit id velit elit. Velit anim eiusmod labore sit amet. Voluptate voluptate irure occaecat deserunt incididunt esse in.
          .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col.mdl-cell--4-col-tablet.mdl-card.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--4dp.portfolio-blog-card-full-bg
            .mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand
            .mdl-card__actions
              span.demo-card-image__filename Pamukkale.jpg
          .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col.mdl-cell--4-col-tablet.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--4dp
            .mdl-card__media
              a(href='#')
                img.article-image(src=' ../images/example-blog04.jpg', border='0', alt='')
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              small Excepteur reprehenderit sint exercitation ipsum consequat qui sit id velit elit.
