                | Velit anim eiusmod labore sit amet. Voluptate voluptate irure occaecat deserunt incididunt esse in. Qui ullamco consectetur aute fugiat officia ullamco proident Lorem ad irure. Sint eu ut consectetur ut esse veniam.
          .demo-card-event.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col.mdl-cell--4-col-tablet.mdl-card.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--4dp.portfolio-blog-card-event-bg.mdl-color-text--white
            .mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand
              h4.mdl-color-text--white
                | Conference event:
                br
                |  May 24, 2016
                br
                |  7-11pm
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-color-text--white Add to Calendar
              .mdl-layout-spacer
              |  
              i.material-icons event
          .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--5-col.mdl-cell--4-col-tablet.mdl-card.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--4dp
